Weather meter components: 

  1. Metal, Waterproof, M20 Cable Gland (6-12mm cable diameter)
  2. Printed Enclosure
  3. 6 wire, 16 Guage, 25' waterproof cable (Black, Red, White, Green, Orange, Yellow) 
  4. Taiss Rotary Encoder 600 P (x2)
  5. 6 pin automotive connector set

Weather Meter Color Coding
  - Direction Encoder
    - Black to Black
    - Red to Red 
    - White to White (pin 13 on lilygo t beam) 
    - Green to Green (pin 2 on lilygo t beam)

  - Speed Encoder
    - Black to Black 
    - Red to Red 
    - Green to Yellow (pin 14 on lilygo t beam)
    - White to orange (pin 25 on lilygo t beam)
